36
00:02:03,058 --> 00:02:04,138
(Shen Wangyan)
I'm Shen Wangyan.

37
00:02:04,338 --> 00:02:05,498
I'm here to work for Mr. Zheng.

38
00:02:05,698 --> 00:02:07,218
Could you please inform him?

39
00:02:08,857 --> 00:02:11,218
Mr. Zheng sold us the mansion
and moved away

40
00:02:11,498 --> 00:02:12,417
a long time ago.

41
00:02:14,018 --> 00:02:15,018
What a pity.

42
00:02:16,417 --> 00:02:19,657
He invited me to visit so many times.

43
00:02:20,778 --> 00:02:22,377
I guess it's not meant to be.

44
00:02:23,377 --> 00:02:26,018
In that case, I'll go somewhere else.

45
00:02:30,778 --> 00:02:32,058
It's raining out there.

46
00:02:32,458 --> 00:02:33,938
How about staying until it stops?

47
00:02:34,298 --> 00:02:35,738
Thank you so much.

48
00:02:42,977 --> 00:02:44,458
Are you here for the test?

49
00:02:44,977 --> 00:02:45,824
Not really.

50
00:02:46,097 --> 00:02:47,938
I ranked third in the Year Jiazi

51
00:02:48,458 --> 00:02:50,018
and went to work for Mr. Huang,

52
00:02:50,018 --> 00:02:51,618
Yangzhou's richest man, as a tutor.

53
00:02:52,178 --> 00:02:54,697
Unfortunately,
he passed away some days ago.

54
00:02:54,697 --> 00:02:55,977
That's why I'm here.

55
00:02:56,377 --> 00:02:57,312
You ranked third?

56
00:02:59,137 --> 00:03:00,257
Then why did you

57
00:03:00,257 --> 00:03:01,137
become a tutor

58
00:03:01,218 --> 00:03:02,257
instead of an official?

59
00:03:03,618 --> 00:03:05,018
I'm from an ordinary family

60
00:03:05,257 --> 00:03:06,178
with no connections

61
00:03:06,577 --> 00:03:08,498
or money to offer
to the Ministry of Personnel.

62
00:03:09,377 --> 00:03:11,377
I became a tutor to make ends meet.

63
00:03:12,577 --> 00:03:14,178
Mr. Zheng is so careless.

64
00:03:14,898 --> 00:03:17,137
Why didn't he tell you that he moved?

65
00:03:17,137 --> 00:03:18,618
You came here in vain.

66
00:03:19,018 --> 00:03:19,936
It's okay.

67
00:03:20,137 --> 00:03:22,338
I know some other
major families in Jianglin.

68
00:03:22,537 --> 00:03:23,377
I'll ask around.

69
00:03:24,377 --> 00:03:25,248
Major families?

70
00:03:26,417 --> 00:03:27,618
Mr. Shen.

71
00:03:28,178 --> 00:03:30,898
