73
00:03:32,657 --> 00:03:33,537
I have a few friends.

74
00:03:34,257 --> 00:03:35,137
Friends?

75
00:03:37,257 --> 00:03:38,498
Banxia, what are you doing?

76
00:03:38,738 --> 00:03:40,377
Bring Mr. Shen some tea.

77
00:03:41,338 --> 00:03:42,458
The rain has stopped.

78
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:43,338
Are you staying?

79
00:03:43,938 --> 00:03:45,178
What kind of question is that?

80
00:03:45,178 --> 00:03:46,048
Just go.

81
00:03:46,738 --> 00:03:48,938
Thank you so much.
I happen to be thirsty.

82
00:03:57,657 --> 00:03:59,498
The tea is burning a bit.

83
00:04:00,618 --> 00:04:01,938
Banxia, what's wrong with you?

84
00:04:03,298 --> 00:04:04,498
It's fine.

85
00:04:05,738 --> 00:04:06,618
Mr. Shen.

86
00:04:07,097 --> 00:04:09,178
You mentioned the major families.

87
00:04:09,778 --> 00:04:11,058
Who do you know

88
00:04:11,058 --> 00:04:12,458
in Jianglin?

89
00:04:13,018 --> 00:04:14,857
You want to meet them?

90
