This is awkward.

91
00:04:19,337 --> 00:04:20,498
I'm trying to marry off

92
00:04:21,098 --> 00:04:22,257
my four daughters.

93
00:04:22,257 --> 00:04:24,978
Mother, don't tell a stranger so much.

94
00:04:24,978 --> 00:04:26,938
Stay quiet or go help your Master.

95
00:04:30,817 --> 00:04:31,697
(I'm not leaving.)

96
00:04:31,858 --> 00:04:33,217
(Let's see what this guy)

97
00:04:33,298 --> 00:04:34,738
(is up to.)

98
00:04:35,577 --> 00:04:37,658
Madam, is your husband an official?

99
00:04:37,658 --> 00:04:39,337
Or what does he do for a living?

100
00:04:40,058 --> 00:04:40,992
How much does he make?

101
00:04:43,217 --> 00:04:44,096
Well...

102
00:04:45,498 --> 00:04:46,978
We only have a pharmacy that makes

103
00:04:46,978 --> 00:04:48,377
a dozen taels per month.

104
00:04:48,817 --> 00:04:49,664
Why are you asking?

105
00:04:50,178 --> 00:04:52,178
A couple should be the right match.

106
00:04:52,418 --> 00:04:53,538
I need information

107
00:04:53,738 --> 00:04:55,098
to help you, Madam.

108
00:04:55,418 --> 00:04:56,337
With what?

109
00:04:56,697 --> 00:04:57,632
Marrying you off.

110
00:04:57,632 --> 00:04:58,528
I don't need it.

111
00:04:58,528 --> 00:04:59,392
Shut up.

112
00:04:59,817 --> 00:05:01,098
Madam, please don't be mad.

113
00:05:01,498 --> 00:05:02,978
I was too direct

114
00:05:03,178 --> 00:05:05,538
and offended her.
Please don't blame her.

115
00:05:06,498 --> 00:05:07,377
You're so polite.

116
00:05:08,418 --> 00:05:09,978
Madam, the rain has stopped.

117
00:05:10,978 --> 00:05:12,058
Thank you for the tea.

118
00:05:12,257 --> 00:05:13,577
Please take care.

119
00:05:16,978 --> 00:05:17,858
Mr. Shen.

120
00:05:18,697 --> 00:05:20,137
You have nowhere to go, anyway.

121
00:05:20,618 --> 00:05:22,697
Why don't you stay here for a few days?

122
00:05:22,697 --> 00:05:23,618
Mother.

123
00:05:23,618 --> 00:05:25,377
We don't have extra rooms for you.

124
00:05:25,377 --> 00:05:26,304
Shut up.

125
00:05:26,538 --> 00:05:27,577
We do.

126
00:05:28,058 --> 00:05:29,538
I hate to bother you.

127
00:05:32,137 --> 00:05:33,088
Oh.

128
00:05:34,017 --> 00:05:36,577
I prepared a gift for Mr. Zheng.

129
00:05:36,577 --> 00:05:37,858
Keep it, Madam.

130
00:05:38,538 --> 00:05:39,777
Thank you.

131
00:05:40,257 --> 00:05:42,098
I hope I can see you around.

132
00:05:42,538 --> 00:05:43,456
I'll take my leave.

133
00:05:58,137 --> 00:05:59,377
He must have written it himself.

134
00:05:59,584 --> 00:06:00,512
(Harmony brings fortune)

135
00:06:00,897 --> 00:06:03,017
Great handwriting.

136
00:06:04,738 --> 00:06:06,178
Are you sure you can tell, Mother?

137
00:06:18,498 --> 00:06:19,938
A-Si is coming back for real.

138
00:06:20,498 --> 00:06:22,697
Come on, Boss, why are you so nervous?

139
00:06:23,017 --> 00:06:23,897
Do I look nervous?

140
00:06:23,897 --> 00:06:25,257
You read the letter ten times.

141
00:06:25,418 --> 00:06:26,298
Are you illiterate?

142
00:06:28,058 --> 00:06:30,137
It just says that A-Si is coming back.

143
00:06:31,137 --> 00:06:32,658
Boss, let me remind you.

144
00:06:33,017 --> 00:06:33,897
Don't beat him

145
00:06:33,897 --> 00:06:35,337
if he confesses to you again.

146
00:06:43,498 --> 00:06:44,858
Can you stop sighing?

147
00:06:44,858 --> 00:06:45,897
It's been a whole day.

148
00:06:45,978 --> 00:06:46,978
Leave me alone.

149
00:06:47,217 --> 00:06:48,137
I'm like a mess.

150
00:06:48,217 --> 00:06:49,120
