155
00:07:09,538 --> 00:07:10,858
Which girl?

156
00:07:11,217 --> 00:07:12,738
Too many girls like me.

157
00:07:12,738 --> 00:07:14,257
The one you're pursuing.

158
00:07:15,498 --> 00:07:16,352
You mean Hua?

159
00:07:17,217 --> 00:07:18,298
How do I put it?

160
00:07:18,498 --> 00:07:20,337
She's pretty and sweet.

161
00:07:20,777 --> 00:07:21,664
I kind of like her.

162
00:07:22,298 --> 00:07:23,178
But I feel that

163
00:07:23,777 --> 00:07:25,978
she's lacking some

164
00:07:26,538 --> 00:07:27,577
