Keling.

183
00:08:46,058 --> 00:08:47,058
Jinrong's clothes...

184
00:08:51,778 --> 00:08:52,778
Ghost!

185
00:08:54,538 --> 00:08:55,497
I don't know anything.

186
00:08:55,497 --> 00:08:56,416
I don't know anything.

187
00:08:56,617 --> 00:08:57,457
- Spare me.
- Hey.

188
00:08:57,817 --> 00:08:59,058
It's talking.

189
00:08:59,337 --> 00:09:00,898
W-Who are you?

190
00:09:01,298 --> 00:09:02,898
It's me. You rascal.

191
00:09:07,778 --> 00:09:08,817
K-Keling.

192
00:09:10,018 --> 00:09:11,778
W-Why are you all made up like that?

193
00:09:13,337 --> 00:09:14,208
I'm not made up.

194
00:09:16,497 --> 00:09:17,538
Right, you're not.

195
00:09:18,097 --> 00:09:19,008
What did you see?

196
00:09:20,258 --> 00:09:23,337
I saw you wearing Jinrong's clothes.

197
00:09:23,617 --> 00:09:24,544
No.

198
00:09:24,857 --> 00:09:26,977
You saw nothing.

199
00:09:27,178 --> 00:09:28,096
Yeah.

200
00:09:28,298 --> 00:09:29,337
I saw nothing.

201
00:09:29,778 --> 00:09:30,720
Get lost.

202
00:09:31,497 --> 00:09:32,416
Okay.

203
00:09:34,817 --> 00:09:36,617
It's okay for girls to dress up

204
00:09:36,697 --> 00:09:37,664
occasionally.

205
00:09:43,298 --> 00:09:44,192
I'm warning you.

206
00:09:45,658 --> 00:09:48,497
If a third person finds out about this,

207
00:09:49,258 --> 00:09:52,298
you'll be buried in our backyard.

208
00:09:53,337 --> 00:09:55,857
Get lost.

209
00:10:05,298 --> 00:10:06,240
Oh no.

210
00:10:06,457 --> 00:10:07,424
Oh no.

211
00:10:11,072 --> 00:10:12,544
