to be very interested

219
00:10:30,538 --> 00:10:31,737
in Miss Jinrong.

220
00:10:32,097 --> 00:10:34,217
I'll find a chance
to arrange for a meeting.

221
00:10:34,817 --> 00:10:35,898
That's great.

222
00:10:36,497 --> 00:10:38,497
Mrs. Chun, you're so blessed.

223
00:10:38,497 --> 00:10:40,058
Mr. Shen, you're so sweet.

224
00:10:40,058 --> 00:10:41,778
Miss Banxia, see you around.

225
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:43,968
So...

226
00:10:43,968 --> 00:10:44,864
Mother.

227
00:10:45,977 --> 00:10:46,848
Banxia.

228
00:10:47,857 --> 00:10:48,737
What are you doing here?

229
00:10:49,977 --> 00:10:50,977
Jinrong may finally

230
00:10:50,977 --> 00:10:52,337
get married.

231
00:10:52,658 --> 00:10:54,018
I'm telling Mr. Shen

232
00:10:54,018 --> 00:10:55,538
about her.

233
00:10:55,776 --> 00:10:56,697
Mother.

234
00:10:56,697 --> 00:10:58,817
Who would help marry off your daughter?

235
00:10:58,817 --> 00:11:00,538
Besides, he's supposed to be a scholar.

236
00:11:00,538 --> 00:11:01,617
Don't get deceived.

237
00:11:02,178 --> 00:11:03,258
Listen to yourself.

238
00:11:03,497 --> 00:11:04,857
Do you think everyone's

239
00:11:04,857 --> 00:11:05,977
as cold as you?

240
00:11:06,298 --> 00:11:07,977
Miss Banxia is very cautious.

241
00:11:08,457 --> 00:11:09,376
Good for her.

242
00:11:09,577 --> 00:11:10,497
Mrs. Chun.

243
00:11:10,497 --> 00:11:12,497
Of course, I'm not helping you for free.

244
00:11:13,497 --> 00:11:14,368
See?

245
00:11:16,697 --> 00:11:17,778
I get it.

246
00:11:19,097 --> 00:11:20,032
Mrs. Chun.

247
00:11:20,217 --> 00:11:21,378
I'm not asking for money.

248
00:11:22,418 --> 00:11:23,296
So...

249
00:11:23,538 --> 00:11:25,298
I don't know where Mr. Zheng is

250
00:11:25,857 --> 00:11:27,097
and I need time to find

251
00:11:27,497 --> 00:11:28,497
someone else to work for.

252
00:11:29,418 --> 00:11:30,304
Mrs. Chun.

253
00:11:31,497 --> 00:11:34,018
I may have to stay
at your mansion for a while.

254
00:11:35,217 --> 00:11:36,258
Oh, come on.

255
00:11:36,418 --> 00:11:38,457
No problem. We have plenty of room.

256
00:11:38,457 --> 00:11:40,977
We have no extra guest room at all.

257
00:11:41,337 --> 00:11:43,097
Mother, let's not bring trouble home.

258
00:11:43,378 --> 00:11:44,778
What are you talking about?

259
00:11:45,258 --> 00:11:46,176
Mr. Shen.

260
00:11:46,258 --> 00:11:48,298
Please help Jinrong find a good man.

261
00:11:48,298 --> 00:11:49,216
Of course.

262
00:11:49,497 --> 00:11:50,400
Mother.

263
00:11:50,497 --> 00:11:51,378
How can you invite

264
00:11:51,378 --> 00:11:52,817
a stranger to live with us?

265
00:11:53,217 --> 00:11:54,457
Shut up.

266
00:11:54,977 --> 00:11:55,936
You...

267
00:11:56,058 --> 00:11:57,857
You're an educated girl.

268
00:11:58,298 --> 00:12:00,058
Mr. Shen ranked third in the test.

269
00:12:00,058 --> 00:12:01,697
"Scholars look at each other", right?

270
00:12:01,898 --> 00:12:04,138
But you're so impolite to him.

271
00:12:04,457 --> 00:12:05,378
Madam,

272
00:12:05,378 --> 00:12:07,577
it should be
"scholars look down on each other".

273
00:12:08,217 --> 00:12:10,538
Yeah, it means scholars don't get along.

274
00:12:17,778 --> 00:12:18,688
So I'll take

275
00:12:19,138 --> 00:12:20,737
Mr. Shen home.
You'll get salted duck eggs.

276
00:12:21,018 --> 00:12:21,920
No way.

277
00:12:22,217 --> 00:12:24,138
Then you can take Mr. Shen home.

278
00:12:24,138 --> 00:12:25,056
No way...

279
00:12:25,538 --> 00:12:26,400
You...

280
00:12:27,138 --> 00:12:28,617
Mrs. Chun, see you later.

281
00:12:28,617 --> 00:12:29,504
See you later.

282
00:12:32,497 --> 00:12:33,337
You can trick my mother,

283
00:12:33,418 --> 00:12:34,304
but not me.

284
00:12:34,577 --> 00:12:35,424
I didn't trick her.

285
00:12:37,058 --> 00:12:38,258
